Arduino Code for Neurophotometrics Fiber Photometry System. Enables user interface and operation of device. More information about Neurophotometrics at https://www.neurophotometrics.com/.

NPM sketches

	- alan1.ino - main sketch for running NPM fiber photometry system

	- alan1.h - header file for main sketch

Libraries - contains necessary libraries for button and LCD

	Button.zip - open source library for interfacing Arduino with buttons

	LiquidCrystal_I2C2004V2.zip - open source library for interfacing Arduino with LCD through I2C pins

PCB files - contains images of PCB layout and schematic in EagleCAD for consecutive design iterations